> Please inline the return value

@terrymanu 
Did you say **inline the return value** like this:
```
    @Override
    public boolean isFirst() throws SQLException {
        boolean first = originalResultSet.isFirst();
        return first;
    }
```
change to ->
```
    @Override
    public boolean isFirst() throws SQLException {
        return originalResultSet.isFirst();
    }
```

